            "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
            "body": "I think this is a duplicate of https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/3944 - we don't use annotations at global scope, mainly because they change the visibility of the variables from outside Cython. I think if you try it as a function argument it'll recognise memoryviews",
